  "texts": [
    "CAVE-based solutions, although proper iVR applications, were excluded due to their high cost, that limits their democratization and general use.",
    "• Papers containing no direct results; for example, if on the design rather than the use of the experience.",
    "• Review articles, comments, editorials, conference records, or any other type of communication other than articles in which experimental results are reported.",
    "• The content of the papers was unrelated to the topic of this review.",
    "• Physiological measurements were not part of the experience."
